videos.headline: Texas Tech scores on blocked punt for first time since '05
videos.description: Texas Tech DE Thomas Leggett powers through the line to block Iowa St. punter Corey Dunn and returns it for a TD.

videos.headline: Iowa State QB Purdy places it perfectly to Kolar for 9-yd TD
videos.description: Iowa State quarterback Brock Purdy threads the needle and delivers to WR Charlie Kolar for a 9-yard touchdown.
